EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
RED FLARE SIGHTED FROM AIRCRAFT VICINITY
58-28N 022-50W AT 230326Z FEB. VESSELS IN
VICINITY REQUESTED TO KEEP A SHARP LOOKOUT,
ASSIST IF POSSIBLE. REPORTS TO UK COAST GUARD,
PHONE: 44 132 631 7575, FAX: 44 132 631 5610,
E-MAIL: FALMOUTHCOASTGUARD@MCGA.GOV.UK.
